CHAT ROOM

this program simulates a chat room between multiple users. Users can either
send private messages or broadcast messages to all online users

Listing of Files:

server_dir/
  makefile - makefile for server
  server.cpp - source file for server
  users.cpp - implementation of user data structure
  users.h - header file for users
  users.txt - recorder users and their passwords

client_dir
  makefile - makefile for client
  client.cpp - source file for client


  How to Run -

  server:
    ./server

  client:
    ./client student02.cse.nd.edu 41046 <username>
